    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Structures containing establishments that chiefly serve beer and simple food, exemplified by large open rooms with communal seating, after the original Bavarian style. These may be temporary structures erected for events or festivals, chiefly Oktoberfest, and usually include facilities for musical entertainment.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
